Grandpa! A rat! A rat!

4
00:04:23,013 --> 00:04:24,431
Kame!

5
00:04:25,849 --> 00:04:27,142
Kametaro!

6
00:05:17,108 --> 00:05:18,527
Brother?

7
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:21,238
Brother!

8
00:05:28,286 --> 00:05:30,163
Uma...

9
00:05:40,257 --> 00:05:42,050
Hide it, brother.

10
00:05:42,175 --> 00:05:44,636
Grandpa will give you hell if he finds it.

11
00:05:45,971 --> 00:05:47,889
How's taro's illness?

12
00:05:48,014 --> 00:05:50,600
He's not eaten since this morning.

13
00:05:52,143 --> 00:05:54,729
There's a curse on him.

14
00:05:55,272 --> 00:05:57,983
You've been to the sea,
haven't you, brother?

15
00:05:58,108 --> 00:05:59,818
No, I haven't.

16
00:05:59,943 --> 00:06:02,237
You're not supposed
to leave the pit at all.

17
00:06:02,362 --> 00:06:05,198
If they find you poaching fish,
they'll kill you.

18
00:06:05,323 --> 00:06:07,158
I haven't been!

19
00:06:07,284 --> 00:06:08,910
I hope not.

20
00:06:09,911 --> 00:06:11,496
Grandpa's coming.

21
00:06:18,044 --> 00:06:20,088
Nekichi?

22
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:22,215
Has uma been here?

23
00:06:23,925 --> 00:06:25,385
I don't know.

24
00:06:37,397 --> 00:06:39,608
Right, kametaro...

25
00:06:43,486 --> 00:06:45,280
Taro! Taro!

26
00:06:50,702 --> 00:06:52,537
- He's better!
- He's better!

27
00:06:55,624 --> 00:06:59,586
Toriko, you mustn't let taro
drink too much water.

28
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:03,757
Uma, you must leave nekichi alone.

29
00:07:04,799 --> 00:07:07,469
I haven't seen him, grandpa.

30
00:07:09,137 --> 00:07:11,973
What would happen
if people found out?

31
00:07:12,098 --> 00:07:14,768
How would you explain it to ryu?

32
00:07:21,191 --> 00:07:22,901
Long ago

33
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:29,616
long ago

34
00:07:29,741 --> 00:07:34,746
very long ago

35
00:07:37,916 --> 00:07:45,423
there came to the kurage sea...

36
00:07:53,890 --> 00:08:01,606
A brother and a sister

37
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:07,570
a god and a goddess

38
00:08:09,364 --> 00:08:17,122
together, they created an island

39
00:08:17,247 --> 00:08:22,002
this is their tale

40
00:08:25,338 --> 00:08:33,304
the tale of how the island began...

41
00:08:41,730 --> 00:08:48,528
Then one day, the god of heaven
called the male god to him.

42
00:08:49,487 --> 00:08:55,410
He told him to become
the guardian deity of an island.

43
00:08:55,535 --> 00:09:01,374
The god of heaven gave him
a bright red rock.

44
00:09:01,499 --> 00:09:04,586
The male god was overjoyed

45
00:09:04,711 --> 00:09:09,007
and threw the rock into the ocean.

46
00:09:09,132 --> 00:09:14,262
It made an enormous splash.

47
00:09:14,387 --> 00:09:16,181
Lo and behold!

48
00:09:16,306 --> 00:09:21,853
All of a sudden, kurage island
appeared in the ocean.

49
00:09:22,854 --> 00:09:24,147
And then what?

50
00:09:24,272 --> 00:09:30,612
And then the male god
tried to go down to the island.

51
00:09:30,737 --> 00:09:33,239
But he couldn't.

52
00:09:33,364 --> 00:09:38,620
"I must get down somehow,
but I can't!"

53
00:09:42,624 --> 00:09:45,752
So he begged the god of heaven,

54
00:09:45,877 --> 00:09:51,424
"I beg you, bestow upon me
the part of my body that I lack."

55
00:09:51,549 --> 00:09:54,636
The god of heaven was astounded
and said,

56
00:09:54,761 --> 00:09:59,015
"what part of your body
do you lack?"

57
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:08,350
”The part of my body
that I lack...

58
00:10:16,116 --> 00:10:24,116
”...is that of a woman

59
00:10:31,256 --> 00:10:39,256
”I lack the body of a woman ”

